original: "Acid can be negated if you are in a boardable vehicle. Oh, me? Don't worry about me. I'm acidproof♪"
translation: “如果你在一辆可登的车上，酸性物质可以被否定。哦，我？别担心我。“我是耐酸的”

original: "All my clothes and so on are made of my cells! It's okay if you touch me more♪"
translation: “我所有的衣服等都是用我的细胞做的！如果你再碰我就好了

original: "Armored zombies are tough against random attacks, but if you're a good trapper, you can penetrate and damage even the strongest armors! Destroying knees with traps is the future!"
translation: “装甲僵尸很难对付随机攻击，但如果你是一个很好的捕猎者，你甚至可以穿透和伤害最强的盔甲！用陷阱破坏膝盖才是未来！”

original: "Blobs, Triffids, Mycus... they are too diffcult for humans to counter. So... let's make a child to fight against them! She'll be as strong as a thousand humans!"
translation: “斑点，三叉戟，八哥。。。它们太难对付人类了。所以。。。让我们做一个孩子来对抗他们！她会像一千个人一样强壮！”

original: "Do you want to lay your head on my lap? It would make me comfortable, too♪"
translation: “你想把头靠在我腿上吗？它也会让我感到舒服

original: "Don't worry, I'm not wearing anything under♪"
"How many children do I want? As many as my master wishes... I will do my best!"
translation: “我要几个孩子？只要我的主人愿意。。。我会尽力的！”

original: "I am a maid♪ Your maid♪ Cleaning, washing, cooking... why didn't you let me continue?"
translation: “我是女佣▪你的女佣▪打扫卫生、洗衣、做饭。。。你为什么不让我继续？”

original: "I can also make furniture and food with my body! ...You don't want any? Oh..."
translation: “我还可以用我的身体做家具和食物！”。。。你不想要吗？哦……”

original: "I dream about Adam and Eve a lot! Let's rebuild humanity with our children, master!"
translation: “我经常梦见亚当和夏娃！让我们和我们的孩子一起重建人性吧，主人！”

original: "I learned that this form of human is the most suitable for service work! How is it? Why do you say it's inferior to my previous form?"
translation: “我了解到，这种形式的人最适合服务工作！怎么样？你为什么说这比我以前的状态差？”

original: "I will continue talking as much as master desires! I will continue talking even if you don't want me to!"
translation: “师父要我说多少我就说多少！即使你不想我说，我也要继续说！”

original: "I'm sorry, master, but... I want to lick it♪"
"If you have a pet carrier, you can store me in it. I am a pet... your pet, master♪"
translation: “如果你有宠物箱，你可以把我放在里面。我是宠物。。。你的宠物，主人

original: "Is it okay for me to die? Yeah, right!♪ Ah, I will fully recover even from the most mortal wounds. Truly, you'd have to kill me down to the molecular level for me to die... That's why you don't have to be worried about me, master♪"
translation: “我死可以吗？是的，对！啊，即使是最致命的创伤，我也会完全康复的。说真的，你必须把我杀到分子水平才能让我死。。。所以你不用担心我，师父

original: "Is it okay to love a shoggoth? Ah, I don't mind the race difference at all! I will always be by my master's side♪"
translation: “爱一只矮脚熊可以吗？啊，我一点也不介意种族差异！我将永远在我主人的身边

original: "It's okay if master gets tied up! That way I can stay by your side as long as I want... Ufufu..."
translation: “师傅被绑了没关系！这样我就可以在你身边想呆多久就呆多久。。。乌夫……”

original: "Mashterr"
"Master gave me my first death. Please allow me to give many things their first death."
translation: “师父让我第一次死。请允许我把他们第一次死的许多东西给他们。”

original: "Master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master master..."
translation: “大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师大师……”

original: "Master! A-ah, my master's thing... tekeli-li! Kya!"
translation: “师父！啊，我主人的事。。。李特克力！凯亚！”

original: "Master! Do you want to hold hands?"
"Master! Master! Are you going to play with the mi-gos?"
translation: “师父！主人！你要和米戈一家玩吗？”

original: "Master!"
"Master!♪"
"Master"
"Master's smell... it's intoxicating... haa, master...♪"
translation: “师父的味道。。。令人陶醉。。。哈，主人…“

original: "Master, are you a lolicon? Or do you like big breasts? If you tell me, I can become more to your liking!♪"
translation: “师父，你是个懒汉吗？还是你喜欢大乳房？如果你告诉我，我会变得更合你的意！♪"

original: "Master, cheating is not okay. Just me, alright?"
translation: “师傅，作弊是不行的。只有我，好吗？”

original: "Master, have you come across any albino penguins? I know them well, because they are my colleagues. Try not to bother them too much. ...Also, their meat doesn't taste too good."
translation: “师父，你见过白化企鹅吗？我很了解他们，因为他们是我的同事。尽量不要打扰他们太多。。。而且，他们的肉味道也不太好。”

original: "Master..."
"Master...♪"
"Master?"
"Master~"
"Master~~"
"Master♪"
"My kind is known to be violent, isn't that right? But you don't have to worry about me. I am a slave to my master's love♪"
translation: “大家都知道我这一类人很暴力，不是吗？但你不用担心我。我是我主人爱的奴隶

original: "No matter the weather, my heart beats on if I'm with my master♪"
translation: “无论天气如何，如果我和我的主人在一起，我的心就会跳动”

original: "Please let me know if you need a bath. I can wrap you up in my body and clean everything from sweat to dirt and make you smell good♪"
translation: “如果你需要洗澡，请告诉我。我可以把你裹在身上，把汗水和污垢都洗干净，让你闻起来很香

original: "Please pass me your dirty clothes. I will keep them clean and beautiful♪"
translation: “请把你的脏衣服递给我。我会保持它们干净美丽

original: "Please use me as a shield in an emergency. I want to be useful and not be like the other shoggoths."
translation: “在紧急情况下，请用我做挡箭牌。我想做个有用的人，而不是像其他人一样。”

original: "Please use me! Why don't you want to use me? Please use me! Use me!"
translation: “请用我！你为什么不利用我？请利用我！利用我！”

original: "Tekeli, tekeli-li! Tekeli, tekeli-li! We'll have a lot of fun when you feel better!"
translation: “特凯利，特凯利！特凯利，特凯利！当你感觉好些的时候，我们会玩得很开心的！”

original: "Tekeli-li! Tekeli-li!"
"Tekeli-li!"
"Tekeli-li?"
"Tekeli-li~♪ Hello, master♪"
"The lingering lightning after an electric shock reaches only one square around! So if you wield a spear and a use a suitable martial art, you can dodge it all! ...I have no idea what I just said."
translation: “电击后的余辉只到达周围一方！所以，如果你挥舞长矛，使用适当的武术，你可以躲过这一切。。。我不知道我刚才说了什么。”

original: "The past cannot be changed. The future may be dark, but I have my master by my side. So, please... please... don't leave me alone."
translation: “过去无法改变。未来可能是黑暗的，但我有我的主人在我身边。所以，请。。。拜托。。。别丢下我一个人。”

original: "This feeling of chasing down mi-gos is becoming addictive...♪"
translation: “这种追米哥的感觉越来越让人上瘾了……”

original: "Those who try to take my master away will turn into minchi!♪"
translation: “那些想带走我主人的人会变成明治！♪"

original: "We'll have as many babies as master wants♪"
"What was his name again? Cthulhu?"
"When I first met master, I thought I had no other choice than to follow this person. I wonder if this is love at first sight? What?"
translation: “当我第一次见到师父的时候，我想我别无选择，只能跟着这个人。不知道这是不是一见钟情？什么？”

original: "Why am I in human form? Well, that's how I can talk to my master, to be able to walk hand in hand with my master and have a body for my master to... nevermind!"
translation: “为什么我是人形？好吧，那就是我能和我的主人说话的方式，能和我的主人手拉手走路，有一个身体让我的主人。。。别客气！”

original: "You've worked really hard! As a reward, I will take you out on a date..."
translation: “你真的很努力！作为奖励，我会带你出去约会……”

original: %1$s tears into %2$s with their monstrous limbs
translation: %1$s人用他们可怕的四肢撕裂%2$s人

original: %s appears more steady and composed.
'Ah... I think I went overboard and turned out like this. I need some time to return to my former shape. Please warm me up in master's pockets! Don't put me in a fridge! Absolutely not!'
translation: “啊。。。我想我太过火了，结果变成这样了。我需要一些时间来恢复我以前的状态。请在主人的口袋里给我暖暖身子！别把我放进冰箱！绝对不是

original: 'What's up? Why haven't you put me on the ground yet? Ah, you want me to stay tiny for a little while longer? Ehh... I suppose it can't be helped.'
translation: “怎么了？你为什么还不把我放在地上？啊，你想让我多呆一会儿吗？呃。。。我想这是没办法的

original: <chitchat_player_responses>
<npcname> assaults %s with fury and dedication
<npcname> lands a measured strike on %s
<npcname> strikes %s in one elegant motion
<npcname> strikes with a malice that surprises you
<npcname> struggles and forces %s back
<shoggoth_chat>
A French maid dress in the modern style, black with a frilly white apron. Doesn't cover much past the thigh or shoulder.
translation: 一种现代风格的法国女仆礼服，黑色，白色褶边围裙。没有太多的覆盖大腿或肩膀。

original: A French maid dress in the modern style, black with a frilly white apron. Doesn't cover much past the thigh or shoulder. Something seems off about it.
translation: 一种现代风格的法国女仆礼服，黑色，白色褶边围裙。没有太多的覆盖大腿或肩膀。好像有点不对劲。

original: A Maid's Memoirs
A Victorian maid dress tailored specifically for post-cataclysm maids. The kevlar weave provides modest protection, but makes it somewhat harder to move in.
translation: 专为大灾变后的女佣量身打造的维多利亚女佣礼服。凯夫拉尔编织提供适度的保护，但使它有点难以移动。

original: A blob shaped like the tail of a cat that has been made docile. Whenever you walk, it sways back and forth. Make sure to feed your new blob friend!
translation: 一种形状象猫尾巴的斑点，被驯服了。无论你走什么时候，它都会前后摇摆。一定要喂饱你的新朋友！

original: A brown soft and furry cat tail. Whenever you walk, it sways back and forth. You can turn it on for extra enjoyment.
translation: 棕色柔软毛茸茸的猫尾巴。无论你走什么时候，它都会前后摇摆。你可以打开它来享受额外的乐趣。

original: A child entrusted to you by the owner of the house you served at. There's a deep feeling of fear in your stomach as you embrace the cataclysm, but protecting this child gives you purpose and makes you feel less alone.
translation: 你服务的房子的主人托付给你的孩子。当你拥抱这场灾难时，你的胃里有一种深深的恐惧感，但是保护这个孩子给了你目标，让你感觉不那么孤独。

original: A classic maid outfit with a white apron, frills and a black one piece. It has some storage space thanks to the apron and side pockets, including space for throwing knives. Since it comes with bloomers, you can take off your underwear and not feel embarrassed about it!
translation: 一套经典的女仆装，白色围裙，褶边和黑色连体衣。由于围裙和侧袋，它有一些存储空间，包括扔刀的空间。因为它与灯笼裤，你可以脱下你的内衣，而不是感到尴尬！

original: A collection of letters written by various maids, detailing the things they do for their masters. The later pages are filled with drawings from what little you can peek, but they're stuck together with something. Can teach you a unique martial art.
translation: 各种女仆写的信的集合，详述她们为主人所做的事情。后面的几页充满了你所能看到的图画，但是它们被一些东西粘在了一起。可以教你一门独特的武术。

original: A crude and simple throwing knife made from a sharpened piece of salvaged steel with cloth wrapped around it. It's better than throwing rocks, at least.
translation: 一种粗糙而简单的飞刀，由一块锋利的打捞上来的钢制成，周围裹着布。至少比扔石头好。

original: A crystallized manifestation of passion. Acts as a source of energy in certain types of tools for maids.
translation: 激情的具体表现。在某些类型的女佣工具中充当能量来源。

original: A frilly white cap commonly used by maids.
translation: 女仆常用的一种有褶边的白色帽子。

original: A frilly white cap commonly used by maids. There's two bumps on top of it that look like cat ears. It's very cute.
translation: 女仆常用的一种有褶边的白色帽子。上面有两个突起看起来像猫耳朵。它很可爱。

original: A frilly white headband commonly used by maids. Something seems off about it.
translation: 女佣常用的白色褶边头带。好像有点不对劲。

original: A full-body tuxedo.  Makes the apocalypse feel a little more classy.
translation: 全身礼服。让《启示录》感觉更优雅一点。

original: A glass flask containing a piece of meat that seems to be growing. Occasionally the piece of meat pulsates.
translation: 装有一块似乎正在生长的肉的玻璃瓶。偶尔这块肉会颤动。

original: A large bag that could fit a person inside. The zipper running across it provides ventilation and you can open and close it from the inside. It can be used as a sleeping bag, as well.
translation: 一个能装人的大袋子。穿过它的拉链提供了通风，你可以从里面打开和关闭它。它也可用作睡袋。

original: A large living mass of meat made alive by the means of alchemy. The twisted, distorted meat lump has a mouth-like organ like that of a human, where it constantly spews poisonous gas and acidic bodily fluids from, while making unpleasant sounds.
translation: 炼金术用炼金术制成的大量活肉。扭曲变形的肉块有一个像人一样的嘴状器官，不断地从中喷出有毒气体和酸性体液，同时发出不愉快的声音。

original: A little maid who has been recently milked. She has a fulfilled expression on her face and her skin is shining. You can milk her again after 23 hours.
translation: 最近挤奶的小女佣。她脸上洋溢着满足的表情，皮肤闪闪发光。你可以在23小时后再给她挤奶。

original: A little maid whose belly and breasts have swollen considerably. She's staring at you with lavishing eyes. You can milk her.
translation: 腹部和胸部肿胀得很厉害的小女仆。她用一双奢华的眼睛盯着你。你可以给她挤奶。

original: A little maid with a growing stomach. She's gently blushing and gently smiling at you. You can milk her after 28 days.
translation: 肚子越来越大的小女仆。她轻轻地脸红，轻轻地对你微笑。你可以在28天后给她挤奶。

original: A matching wooden handle and scabbard, concealing a full length katana blade. It appears as a solid wooden stick to those unfamiliar with it, due to how well the handle and scabbard fit together. Activate to unsheath.
translation: 一个匹配的木柄和剑鞘，隐藏着全长武士刀刀片。对于那些不熟悉它的人来说，它看起来像一根结实的木棍，因为刀柄和刀鞘配合得很好。激活以取消阴影。

original: A matching wooden handle and scabbard, concealing a full length katana blade. It appears as a solid wooden stick to those unfamiliar with it, due to how well the handle and scabbard fit together. The reinforced wooden sheath makes a decent secondary weapon, though they do, of course, take up more space stored separately.
translation: 一个匹配的木柄和剑鞘，隐藏着全长武士刀刀片。对于那些不熟悉它的人来说，它看起来像一根结实的木棍，因为刀柄和刀鞘配合得很好。强化木鞘是一种不错的辅助武器，当然，它们会占用更多单独储存的空间。

original: A metal rake suitable for combat. The teeth are barbed and serrated. What kind of garden needs a rake like this?
translation: 适于战斗的金属耙子。牙齿有倒刺和锯齿。什么样的花园需要这样的耙子？

original: A mop with a wooden handle that actually conceals a steel core, making it a formidable weapon for taking out whatever trash may pose a threat to your master.
translation: 木柄拖把，实际上隐藏着一个钢芯，使它成为一个可怕的武器，无论垃圾可能会对你的主人构成威胁。

original: A mutagenic serum, designed to transform the subject into a docile servant capable of producing large amounts of milk. Talk to a follower to use.
translation: 一种诱变剂血清，用于将受试者转变成能产生大量牛奶的温顺仆人。与追随者交谈以使用。

original: A mysterious scroll used to summon some kind of mystery meat and drinking water. It can be used multiple times.
translation: 用来召唤某种神秘肉类和饮用水的神秘卷轴。可以多次使用。

original: A nimble blade meant for ranged assassination, but makes an improvised cutlery tool in a pinch. It's very lightweight and silent and can be used on both zombies and games involving apples.
translation: 一种灵活的刀锋，用于远程暗杀，但在紧急情况下可作为一种简易的餐具。它非常轻巧和安静，可以用于僵尸和涉及苹果的游戏。

original: A regular maid's white brim with an elegant veil sewn into it, decorated with silver frills. Although it covers your eyes and blocks your vision quite harshly, you can use maid points to turn it on and gain otherwordly sight.
translation: 一种普通女仆的白色帽檐，上面缝着一层优雅的面纱，饰以银色的镶边。虽然它覆盖你的眼睛和阻挡你的视线相当严厉，你可以使用女仆点打开它，并获得其他视觉。

original: A regular maid's white brim with an elegant veil sewn into it, decorated with silver frills. It is currently see-through.
translation: 一种普通女仆的白色帽檐，上面缝着一层优雅的面纱，饰以银色的镶边。它目前是透明的。

original: A semi-crystallized manifestation of passion, not yet fully catalyzed into a usable form.
translation: 激情的一种半结晶的表现形式，尚未完全催化成可用的形式。

original: A set of pure white stockings with garterbelt and panties, decorated with elegant lacing.
translation: 一套纯白长袜配吊袜带和内裤，饰以优雅的花边。

original: A set of scrolls and sacrifices used to summon a different kind of maid. Pour the sacrificial sugar in the middle of the magic circle and cast the correct spell.
translation: 用来召唤不同类型女仆的一套卷轴和祭品。把牺牲糖倒在魔法圈中间，施放正确的咒语。

original: A set of secret maid cookware. By powering it with maid energy, you can create dishes filled with love.
translation: 一套女仆秘制炊具。通过女仆能量，你可以创造充满爱的菜肴。

original: A shiny black cat tail made out of leather. Whenever you walk, it sways back and forth. You can turn it on for extra enjoyment.
translation: 一条由皮革制成的发亮的黑色猫尾巴。无论你走什么时候，它都会前后摇摆。你可以打开它来享受额外的乐趣。

original: A shoggoth mimicking the look of an attractive maid. Contrary to the neat appearance, her head has swirls of pink and iridescent colors swirling around. She has a deep seated love for her master.
translation: 模仿漂亮女佣的长相。与整洁的外表相反，她的头上有粉红色和彩虹色的漩涡。她深深地爱着她的主人。

original: A small maid summoned from a different world. Although difficult to have a conversation with, it seems she had longed to be summoned.
translation: 从另一个世界召唤来的小女仆。虽然很难与她交谈，但她似乎渴望被召唤。

original: A special type of underwear meant for people with tails. Although it's incredibly thin, it's the last line of defense for your dignity.
translation: 为有尾巴的人准备的一种特殊内衣。虽然它非常薄，但它是你尊严的最后一道防线。

original: A special type of underwear meant for people with tails. It stands as the difference between being a gentleman and being a beast.
translation: 为有尾巴的人准备的一种特殊内衣。这是绅士和野兽的区别。

original: A strange frying pan that smells of rotting fish. Indigo flames dance faintly beneath the finish. When activated, it will be wreathed in fire.
translation: 一种奇怪的煎锅，闻起来有腐烂的鱼的味道。靛蓝的火焰在终点下隐约舞动。当激活时，它将被火焰包围。

original: A strange kitchen knife. The patterns on the blade bring unpleasant thoughts to mind. When activated, it can drain strength from enemies.
translation: 一把奇怪的菜刀。刀刃上的图案让人想起不愉快的想法。激活后，它可以消耗敌人的力量。

original: A summoned little maid. She looks and wanders around while holding onto the hem of your clothes tightly. She's afraid of fighting.
translation: 一个被召唤的小女仆。她环顾四周，紧紧抓住你衣服的下摆。她害怕打架。

original: A thin leaflet that's filled with chaotic handwriting, disturbing visuals, impossible mathematical equations, languages not known to anyone on Earth and lists of what appears to be names with all of them crossed out. The leaflet has more pages than possible, each and every one of them getting more and more chaotic and giving you a splitting headache as the fabric of reality seems to collapse around your vision. Suddenly, it's all clear to you. On the final page, you read a complex formula on how to summon a shoggoth, seemingly written in your handwriting.
translation: 一张薄薄的传单，上面写满了混乱的笔迹、令人不安的视觉效果、不可能的数学方程式、地球上任何人都不知道的语言，以及似乎是名字的清单，所有这些都被划掉了。传单的页数比可能的多，每一页都变得越来越混乱，让你头痛欲裂，因为现实的结构似乎在你的视野周围崩溃。突然，你就明白了。在最后一页，你读到了一个复杂的公式如何召唤一个shoggoth，似乎写在你的手写。

original: A tux tailored specifically for post-cataclysm butlers. The kevlar weave provides modest protection, but makes it somewhat harder to move in.

original: 你有个女仆。因为你的健康，她被你父亲雇来保护你的安全。她很漂亮而且。。。她很会打架。然而，她一直在说'主人！我已经摆脱了所有的怪物！这是做爱的最佳时机！让我们一起生很多孩子吧！“。。。她有点古怪。
